Requirements
==========
Ubuntu: sudo apt update -y && sudo apt install build-essential cmake ncurses-dev -y
Fedora: sudo dnf upgrade -y && sudo dnf group install c-development -y && sudo dnf install cmake ncurses-devel -y

Steps
==========
1) cd <path_to_source>
2) mkdir build && cd build
3) cmake -S .. -B .
4) make -j$(nproc)
